{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab If there's a company you really like but the job description doesn't suit you, consider applying anyway. There may be a job you prefer in the future with them.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Medical certs are needed where an interview is missed due to ill health. Notify the work placement manage or career services immediately by telephone if you can't attend the interview.\par}
